description:
John Doe of X talks about his 1970s Guild D-35 acoustic guitar
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube 

John Doe of the legendary Los Angeles band X talks about his 1970s Guild D-35 acoustic guitar. "This is my folky guitar," Doe says. "A lot of the blues players back in the '50s, '60s, '70s, played Guilds, and I didn't know that when I got it. I just liked the way it sounded."

@GuildGuitarsUSA
